sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Flutter Client
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth
    participant DB as Cloud Storage (Firestore/Supabase)

    User->>App: Input Credentials (Email/Password)
    App->>Auth: Authentication Request (API Call)
    Note right of Auth: Verifying Password Hash
    Auth-->>App: Session Token (JWT / ID Token)
    Note over App: Validating Token & Initializing Session
    
    App->>DB: Authorized Data Request (with JWT)
    Note right of DB: Firestore Security Rules Check
    DB-->>App: Encrypted JSON Response (Data)
    App-->>User: Secured Dashboard View
